0. Install Android SDK and Android NDK

NDK must be downloaded separately from:

http://dl.google.com/android/ndk/

and then installed somewhere.

1. Make sure that ~/Eclipse/android-sdk-mac_x86/platform-tools/ and XXX-NDK-BUILD-PATH are in the PATH variable in your ~/.profile directory.

2. Get batphone source code to use as basis of energy measurement framework:
git clone git://github.com/servalproject/batphone.git -b wifi-autodetect

3. Build batphone for the first time:
cd batphone
./BUILD.txt
